Product description

Perfectly for adding efficient storage capacity and it is convenient for you to place the items, such as pens, glasses, coins, sweets, business cards, phones, etc. It keeps everything organized and easily accessible

You're going to absolutely Love PIMCAR Upgraded Center Console Organizer, Because

If your gear is cluttering up the center console of your Silverado / Sierra, it can become damaged rolling around. It’s hard to find items when they’re clumped together in a messy pile. But where can you organize and store a lot of gear within the confines of your truck?

Here, PIMCAR gives you an effective way to use it and organize your gear with this Silverado / Sierra center console organizer.


Without

Without the organizer, make your center console just like a large deep black hole.


Messy

Everything is hard to access and the small item will be vibration and make noise while driving.


Organized

Fits perfectly in the console and still allows for access to the bottom, the rubber mats in each compartment are removable for cleaning. It always helps you maintain a clean car interior environment.

Features & details

Features

  • For CHEVY SILVERADO: Fits for 2019-2022 Chevy Silverado 1500 and 2020-2022 Chevy Silverado 2500 HD/3500 HD, including LT, LTZ, Trail Boss, RST, and High Country (Full console w/bucket seats ONLY)
  • For GMC SIERRA: Fits for 2019-2022 GMC Sierra 1500 and 2020-2022 GMC Sierra 2500 HD/3500 HD, including SLE, SLT, Elevation, AT4, and Denali (Full console w/bucket seats ONLY)
  • EXTRA SPACE: This center console tray provides a significant storage area in the console of the truck. It can make items organized like wallets, cell phones, sunglasses, lipsticks, keys, coins, and other small items.
  • HIGH QUALITY: This center console tray is made of high-quality ABS plastic material with a matte finish and non-slip rubber pads which keep things from sliding around and rattling inside.
  • EASY INSTALLATION: No tools or adhesive required, put the tray directly into the center console. Easy to take in and out in seconds.
